Package org.rsna.ctp.stdstages.storage

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AjaxServlet
    A Servlet which provides web access to the index data in a FileStorageService.
    FileSystem
    A class to encapsulate Study objects in a single FileSystem.
    FileSystemManager
    A class to keep track of FileSystems.
    GuestList
    A class to encapsulate a set of users who have been invited to access a FileSystem.
    GuestListServlet
    A Servlet which provides web access to the studies stored in a FileStorageService.
    ImageQualifiers
    A class encapsulating the selection of frames as well as size and quality parameters of images..
    StorageMonitor
    The Thread that automatically removes studies from the storage service after they time out.
    StorageServlet
    A Servlet which provides web access to the studies stored in a FileStorageService.
    StoredObject
    A class to encapsulate the File and URL of a stored object.
    Study
    A class to manage the FileObjects in a single study.
